OL,3,CWelsh FM accused of doing 'nothing' to
OL,4,Cprotect pensioners from winter fuel cut
OL,6,FThe First Minister of Wales has been
OL,7,Faccused of doing "absolutely nothing"
OL,8,Fto protect pensioners, following a UK
OL,9,FGovernment U-turn on winter fuel
OL,10,Fpayment cuts.
OL,12,FDarren Millar, leader of the Welsh
OL,13,FConservatives, called for Eluned
OL,14,FMorgan to apologise to the pensioners
OL,15,Faffected by the change last winter,
OL,16,Farguing the Welsh Government should
OL,17,Fhave stepped in to support those in
OL,18,Fneed.
