OL,3,CWelsh FM accused of doing 'nothing' to
OL,4,Cprotect pensioners from winter fuel cut
OL,6,FSpeaking during First Minister's
OL,7,FQuestions on Tuesday, Mr Millar said
OL,8,Fthe cut had forced vulnerable people
OL,9,Fto choose between heating and eating.
OL,11,FEluned Morgan, leader of the Welsh
OL,12,FLabour Government, said she was
OL,13,F"absolutely delighted" that the UK
OL,14,FGovernment had reversed the cut for
OL,15,Fmany.
OL,17,FThe payment, worth up to #300, will be
OL,18,Frestored to the vast majority of
OL,19,Fpensioners, with anyone with an income
OL,20,Fof under #35,000 a year now getting
OL,21,Fthe payment automatically.
