OL,3,CWelsh FM accused of doing 'nothing' to
OL,4,Cprotect pensioners from winter fuel cut
OL,6,FThe decision last July to restrict the
OL,7,Fwinter fuel payment to the poorest
OL,8,Fpensioners was intended to save around
OL,9,F#1.5 billion a year, with more than
OL,10,Fnine million people who would have
OL,11,Fpreviously been eligible losing out.
OL,13,FRachel Reeves, the Chancellor,
OL,14,Fannounced the partial U-turn on
OL,15,FMonday, following significant backlash
OL,16,Ffrom charities, opposition MPs and the
OL,17,FGovernment's own backbenchers.
