OL,3,CWelsh FM accused of doing 'nothing' to
OL,4,Cprotect pensioners from winter fuel cut
OL,6,FSpeaking in the Senedd, Mr Millar
OL,7,Fsaid, "Yesterday we saw a screeching U-
OL,8,Fturn on the winter fuel allowance by
OL,9,FRachel Reeves, after considerable
OL,10,Fpressure from the Conservative Party.
OL,12,F"You will know that over half a
OL,13,Fmillion Welsh pensioners were deprived
OL,14,Fof their winter fuel payments last
OL,15,Fyear, leaving some very vulnerable
OL,16,Fpeople with the unenvious choice of
OL,17,Fhaving to choose between heating and
OL,18,Feating ` it's an absolute disgrace.
