OL,3,CWelsh FM accused of doing 'nothing' to
OL,4,Cprotect pensioners from winter fuel cut
OL,6,F"You are meant to stand up for Wales
OL,7,Fbut what did you actually do in terms
OL,8,Fof this winter fuel allowance? You did
OL,9,Fabsolutely nothing."
OL,11,FMr Millar argued Eluned should have
OL,12,Fimplemented a Welsh winter fuel
OL,13,Fpayment or stood up to Sir Keir
OL,14,FStarmer and demanded the payment be
OL,15,Frestored sooner.
