OL,3,CWelsh FM accused of doing 'nothing' to
OL,4,Cprotect pensioners from winter fuel cut
OL,6,FEluned Morgan responded "I'm really
OL,7,Fpleased that because we have made
OL,8,Frepresentations to the Prime Minister
OL,9,Fon this issue that he has changed his
OL,10,Fmind and that will make a difference
OL,11,Fto hundreds of thousands of pensioners
OL,12,Facross Wales this winter.
OL,14,F"I don't think that it's bad to listen
OL,15,Fto people and then to make sure that
OL,16,Fyou respond to them."
