OL,3,CWelsh FM accused of doing 'nothing' to
OL,4,Cprotect pensioners from winter fuel cut
OL,6,FEluned Morgan had previously pushed
OL,7,Fback against the cut, having called
OL,8,Ffor a "rethink" in early May, saying
OL,9,Fit was something "that comes up time
OL,10,Fand again".
OL,12,FAt the time, the Government said there
OL,13,Fwould "not be a change to the
OL,14,FGovernment's policy".
OL,16,FOn 9 June, Ms Reeves suggested that
OL,17,Fthe "stability we've brought back to
OL,18,Fthe economy" meant the Government was
OL,19,Fable to change the eligibility
OL,20,Fthreshold for winter fuel payments.
